<h4>GoCD configuration under SCM (a.k.a Config repositories)</h4>
<p>
  Manage pipeline configurations from one or more source-control repositories (think "git repository") and modify them externally.
  You can watch a quick demo of this feature <a href="http://youtu.be/1AfBxCWRqD8">here</a>
</p>

